text:
Good work, Mamimi.
The event turned out great!

Haha... as always, very Mamimi-like.
You looked very composed up on stage as well.

Do you have any impressions or anything?
Did you get nervous perhaps, or super excited perhaps?
Oh, did you think of something?

Now that you mention it,
When I was on stage...

All of the way in the back, behind the spectators,
I could see you with a worried look on your face.

No, 
I mean, putting me aside for now...

Fufuu... But, I think that might've been the reason
that I could keep my composure.
